            <fr:meta name="postdoc-advisor">larsbirkedal</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Associate Professor in Logical Foundations and Formal Methods at University of Cambridge. Formerly a <fr:link href="jms-0061.xml" title="TypeSynth: synthetic methods in program verification" addr="jms-0061" type="local">Marie Skłodowska-Curie Postdoctoral Fellow</fr:link> hosted at <fr:link href="jms-00GC.xml" title="Aarhus University" addr="jms-00GC" type="local">Aarhus University</fr:link> by <fr:link href="larsbirkedal.xml" title="Lars Birkedal" addr="larsbirkedal" type="local">Lars Birkedal</fr:link>, and before this a PhD student of <fr:link href="robertharper.xml" title="Robert Harper" addr="robertharper" type="local">Robert Harper</fr:link>.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>I am a Bye-Fellow of <fr:link href="jms-00GP.xml" title="Clare College" addr="jms-00GP" type="local">Clare College</fr:link> from February 2024, and have been elected a Fellow for the coming year.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
